In the MATTER OF the PETITION FOR REINSTATEMENT OF Keith Eric TIMMONS to the Bar of Maryland Misc. Docket AG No. 56, Sept. Term, 2016 Court of Appeals of Maryland. November 14, 2016

ORDER

The Court having considered the Petition for Reinstatement of Keith Eric Timmons filed in the above captioned case, it is this 14th day of November, 2016

ORDERED, by the Court of Appeals of Maryland, that the petition be, and it is hereby, GRANTED, and the Petitioner, Keith Eric Timmons is hereby reinstated by this Court to the practice of law in Maryland, and it is further

ORDERED that the Clerk of this Court shall replace the name of Keith Eric Timmons on the register of attorneys in this Court and certify that fact to the Trustees of the Client Protection Fund and the Clerks of all judicial tribunals in this State.
